《科学怪人》于1997年11月30日通过[[福斯广播公司|福克斯电视网]]在美国首播，再于1998年3月29日经[[天空第一台|天空第一台]]在英国播映<ref name="Meisler-1999" />{{rp|84–85}}<ref name="DVDliner">{{Cite AV media notes | title = The X-Files: The Complete Fifth Season | year = 1997–1998 | others = R. W. Goodwin, et al. | type = booklet | publisher = Fox}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | year = 1998 | last1 = Cornell | first = Paul | last2 = Day | first2 = Martin | last3 = Topping | first3 = Keith | title = X-Treme Possibilities | url = https://archive.org/details/xtremepossibilit00corn | publisher = Virgin Publications, Ltd | isbn = 9780753502280 | page = [https://archive.org/details/xtremepossibilit00corn/page/390 390]}}</ref>节目的[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森家庭收视比率]]为11.5，收视率16，意即所有装有电视的美国家庭中有11.5%收看本集，当时就在看电视的观众则有16%选择《科学怪人》，观众总人数约为1868万<ref name="Meisler-1999" />{{rp|284}}，在该周美国所有电视节目中排第十一<ref>{{cite news | title = Prime-Time Ratings | publisher = Freedom Communications | url = http://iw.newsbank.com/resources/doc/nb/news/0EAF418A05CE1193?p=AWNB | accessdate = 2016-10-29 | newspaper = The Orange County Register | date = 1997-12-03}} {{Subscription required}}</ref>。

=== 评价 ===
本集获得评论界的普遍好评。[[奈特里德|奈特里德]]通讯员迈克·达菲（{{lang|en|Mike Duffy}}）对剧集整体持正面态度，称节目虽然颇为特别，但不会让人感觉这都是哗众取宠的鬼花招。他在文中写道：“许多节目都喜欢大放‘非常特别的剧集’这类宣传烟雾，但其中难免会有好莱坞的故弄玄虚，仿佛华而不实大吹法螺的鬼花招。但事实证明，这部略有经典恐怖片《科学怪人》痕迹、号称‘非常特别黑白剧集’的作品实际效果甚佳，《{{lang|en|X}}档案》主创人克里斯·卡特把这个故事讲述得精彩纷呈。”<ref name="Duffy">{{cite news | last = Duffy | first = Mike | title = Special 'X-Files' Episode Just That | url = http://iw.newsbank.com/resources/doc/nb/news/0EB595F0762E98FE?p=AWNB | accessdate = 2016-10-30 | newspaper = Columbus Ledger-Enquirer | date = 1997-11-29 | publisher = Knight Ridder | pages = A8}}{{Subscription required}}</ref>《[[新闻登记报|莫比尔登记报]]》（{{lang|en|''Mobile Register''}}）发文称，《科学怪人》“同《{{lang|en|X}}档案》最优异的剧集一样，将恐怖同大量幽默融为一体<ref>{{cite news | title = 'X-Files' Spoofs Horror Classics | url = http://iw.newsbank.com/resources/doc/nb/news/0FB2F1334DE62D68?p=AWNB | accessdate = 2016-10-31 | newspaper = Mobile Register | publisher = Advance Publications | date = 1997-11-30 | page = 8}} {{Subscription required}}</ref>。”《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的迈克尔·索特（{{lang|en|Michael Sauter}}）在回顾第五季时称赞《科学怪人》是其中“最动人的”独立剧集<ref name="Sauter">{{cite news | last = Sauter | first = Michael | title = The X-Files: The Complete Fifth Season | newspaper = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Inc. | date = 2002-05-14 | archivedate = 2016-03-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330100609/http://www.ew.com/article/2002/05/14/x-files-complete-fifth-season | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2002/05/14/x-files-complete-fifth-season | accessdate = 2016-10-31}}</ref>。托德·范德韦尔夫给予本集的评分为“{{lang|en|A}}”（最高{{lang|en|A}}+）<ref name="av" />，在他看来，虽然剧情有些“愚蠢”，大部分人物都流于俗套，但节目依然令人满意<ref name="av" />。弗朗西斯·达斯（{{lang|en|Francis Dass}}）于2000年在《[[新海峡时报|新海峡时报]]》（{{lang|en|''New Straits Times''}}）发文，称赞《科学怪人》是“有趣的剧集<ref name="Dass">{{cite news | last = Dass | first = Francis | title = A Late 'X-Files' Collection | newspaper = New Straits Times | publisher = New Straits Times Press | date = 2000-04-20 | accessdate = 2016-10-31 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LdIVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=iBQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3817,882603 | archive-date = 2021-04-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210423111648/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LdIVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=iBQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3817%2C882603 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。”

《沙山记者报》（{{lang|en|''Sand Mountain Reporter''}}）的莱昂内尔·格林（{{lang|en|Lionel Green}}）称本集是《{{lang|en|X}}档案》最佳剧集，拥有“全剧最令人振奋的结局之一<ref>{{cite news | last = Green | first = Lionel | title = 'The X-Files' Was a Rare Magic | url = http://iw.newsbank.com/resources/doc/nb/news/12220EF96B1AE1B0?p=AWNB | accessdate = 2016-10-31 | newspaper = Sand Mountain Reporter | publisher = Southern Newspapers | date = 2008-07-22}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。”埃里克·明克在《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》撰文，给予本集四星评价，称其是表现相对薄弱的前五季中最出彩的其中一集，还赞扬两位主角的演出完美无缺，克里斯·欧文斯对穆塔托的诠释更是感人。在他看来，“有雪莱的经典作品珠玉在前，卡特和福克斯公司又创作出他们自己的经典<ref name="Mink">{{cite news | last = Mink | first = Eric | title = 'X-Files' is Still a Monster  | newspaper = [[纽约每日新闻|Daily News]] | publisher = Mortimer Zuckerman | date = 1997-11-27 | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/x-files-monster-article-1.773122 | archivedate = 2016-10-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161031032927/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/x-files-monster-article-1.773122 | accessdate = 2016-10-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。”《[[科珀斯克里斯蒂来电时报|科珀斯克里斯蒂来电时报]]》（{{lang|en|''Corpus Christi Caller-Times''}}）的伊莱恩·莱纳尔（{{lang|en|Elaine Linere}}）觉得《科学怪人》的剧本堪称“神来之笔”，即便是在这部一直引人入胜、坚持创新的电视剧中也堪称经典，还特别称赞节目“感人而浪漫”的结局<ref>{{cite news | last = Liner | first = Elaine | title = 'X-Files' Marks the Spot Once Again – Tale of Alien Encounter Proves Show's Classiness | publisher = E. W. Scripps Company | newspaper = Corpus Christi Caller-Times | url = http://iw.newsbank.com/resources/doc/nb/news/11A543FDCE798548?p=AWNB | accessdate = 2016-10-31 | date = 1997-11-29}}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Boston Globe''}}）的马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）称本集自始至终都令人难忘，其中非凡的视觉特效和黑白镜头营造的独特气氛值得称道<ref name="boston" />。吉尔伯特还特别称赞卡特在剧本创作和执导方面的贡献，称他在戏剧冲突、不着痕迹的幽默和难以捉摸的机智之间保持良好平衡<ref name="boston" />。《[[纽约_(杂志)|纽约]]》（{{lang|en|''New York''}}）杂志刊出玛格丽特·莱昂斯（{{lang|en|Margaret Lyons}}）的评论，称《科学怪人》身处历史上最优秀的电视剧集之列<ref>{{cite news | last = Lyons | first = Margaret | title = Breaking Bad's Biggest X-Files Allusion Yet | publisher = New York Media, LLC | url = http://www.vulture.com/2012/07/breaking-bad-x-files-house-tent-mutato.html | accessdate = 2016-10-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160129104042/http://www.vulture.com/2012/07/breaking-bad-x-files-house-tent-mutato.html | newspaper = New York | date = 2012-07-30 | archivedate = 2016-01-29 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[帝国杂志|帝国杂志]]》的尼克·德赛姆伦（{{lang|en|Nick De Semlyen}}）和詹姆斯·怀特（{{lang|en|James White}}）把本集在《{{lang|en|X}}档案》所有剧集中排名第五，称赞卡特“玩出风格、玩出花样，把整集转变成向所有怪物电影充满爱意的致敬，特别是詹姆斯·惠尔1931年版的《科学怪人》<ref>{{cite web | last2 = White | first2 = James | date = 2013-10 | archivedate = 2016-04-20 | url = http://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/greatest-x-files-episodes/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160420181339/http://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/greatest-x-files-episodes/ | title = The 20 Greatest X-Files Episodes | work = [[帝国杂志|Empire]] | publisher = Bauer Media Group | last1 = Semlyen | first1 = Nick De | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-04-20}}</ref>。”1999年，{{lang|en|[[FX_(电视频道)|FX]]}}在[[感恩节|感恩节]]连续播映剧迷推选的《{{lang|en|X}}档案》剧集，其中《科学怪人》是“最佳独立剧集”<ref>{{cite AV media | title = The X-Files Thanksgiving Marathon (November 25, 1999) | medium = TV | publisher = [[FX_(电视频道)|FX]]}}</ref>《[[迈阿密先驱报|迈阿密先驱报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Miami Herald''}}）的康妮·奥格勒（{{lang|en|Connie Ogle}}）称穆塔托是《{{lang|en|X}}档案》历史上“最伟大的怪物”之一<ref>{{cite news | last = Ogle | first = Connie | title = The X-Factor: As 'I Want to Believe' Hits Theaters, We Look Back at 'The X-Files' Greatest Monsters | url = http://iw.newsbank.com/resources/doc/nb/news/122255E7DB9EE858?p=AWNB | accessdate = 2016-10-31 | newspaper = The Miami Herald | publisher = The McClatchy Company | date = 2008-07-25}}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。

[[罗伯特·谢尔曼|罗伯特·谢尔曼]]（{{lang|en|Robert Shearman}}）和[[拉斯·皮尔逊|拉斯·皮尔逊]]（{{lang|en|Lars Pearson}}）的著作《希望相信：{{lang|en|X}}档案批判指南，千禧年与孤胆枪手》（{{lang|en|''Wanting to Believe: A Critical Guide to The X-Files, Millennium & The Lone Gunmen''}}）对本集评分不佳，仅有两星（最高五星），对剧中多种要素提出批评。书中称，克里斯·卡特的剧本构想虽融轻松、俏皮和魅力于一身，但他的导演水平显然没有跟上，导致节目太着痕迹而且非常枯燥，变得索然无味。<ref name="Shearman">{{Cite book | year = 2009 | first1 = Robert | last1 = Shearman | first2 = Lars | last2 = Pearson | title = Wanting to Believe: A Critical Guide to The X-Files, Millennium & The Lone Gunmen | publisher = Mad Norwegian Press | isbn = 9780975944691 | pages = 128–129}}</ref>两人称赞剧中镇民仿佛《{{lang|en|X}}档案》观众的构思，但对漫画书式的背景设定不以为然，觉得这样的后现代主义风格未免不合情理，因为漫画中有动作，是用动作来实现画面过渡，但电视剧中这样处理却只能显现出懒惰和自我放纵<ref name="Shearman" />。《{{lang|en|[[Cinefantastique|Cinefantastique]]}}》杂志的保拉·维塔里斯（{{lang|en|Paula Vitaris}}）对节目的评价也不佳，评分一星半（最高四星）<ref name="cinepaula">{{cite journal | last = Vitaris | first = Paula | title = Fifth Season Episode Guide | journal = Cinefantastique | date = 1998-10 | volume = 30 | issue = 7/8 | pages = 29–50}}</ref>。在她看来，剧中空有大堆情境和惯例，但这些内容间缺乏联系，导致情节流于形式，无法达成理想的情绪效果<ref name="cinepaula" />。她还批评剧中把各个角色同多种动物相比较的桥段，觉得镜头有些过火<ref name="cinepaula" />，并且最终的结局太做作，缺乏真情实感<ref name="cinepaula" />。

=== 荣誉 ===
《科学怪人》在1998年的第50届黄金时段艾美奖角逐中获七项提名，除克里斯·卡特获杰出导演和编剧奖提名外，还有艺术指导、摄影、单剧剪辑、化妆和配乐奖提名，最终格雷姆·穆雷（{{lang|en|Graeme Murray}}）、格雷格·洛温（{{lang|en|Greg Loewen}}）和雪莉·英格特（{{lang|en|Shirley Inget}}）拿下艺术指导奖。此外，卡特还获得[[美国导演协会|美国导演协会]]的杰出导演奖提名。<ref name="Meisler-1999" />{{rp|282}}

